{"word":"G1937 - ἐπιθυμέω - epithyméō - ep-ee-thoo-meh'-o - Covet","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιθυμέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epithyméō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-thoo-meh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Covet</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விரும்பு, ஆசையாயிரு, இச்சி"},{"paragraph":"to have a desire for, long for"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G2372 - θυμός - thymós - thoo-mos'/2372\">G2372</a>; to set the <i>heart upon</i>, that is, <i>long</i> for (rightfully or otherwise): - covet, desire, would fain, lust (after).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1760/1760\">G1760</a>, <a href=\"#/G1761/1761\">G1761</a>, <a href=\"#/G1937/1937\">G1937</a>, <a href=\"#/G1938/1938\">G1938</a>, <a href=\"#/G1939/1939\">G1939</a>, <a href=\"#/G2372/2372\">G2372</a>"}]}